      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is looking for a new home and a little extra TLC to get back to its best. While it's currently in poor condition and will need some dedicated mechanical or body work, it serves as a fantastic affordable entry point or a valuable source for parts. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your next great success story!",
