    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone looking for a solid daily driver. While the mechanical components are sound and the car runs well, there are some visible cosmetic imperfections including a few noticeable scratches on the body and some minor wear on the interior upholstery. It has been regularly serviced, though it does show its age in terms of exterior finish. This is an ideal choice for a buyer who values utility and mechanical consistency over a showroom-perfect appearance.",
      "price": 19500.0,
