    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine starts promptly and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides reliable shifting across all gears. While the car shows some minor signs of regular use on the interior and exterior, it remains a dependable and comfortable choice for a daily driver. All major systems are functional, and it is ready for its next owner without any immediate need for significant repairs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
